{"tid":2074294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"軍情動態》威懾中國北韓 美國3航艦現蹤菲律賓海","createTime":"2020-06-22T04:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T09:05:36.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"808e5693e8a33e8694b186ffd6b1ff0f23b8b7f9","tid":2074294,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:03:18.000Z","msg":"軍情動態》威懾中國北韓 美國3航艦現蹤菲律賓海<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3205132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3205132&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=977dcf06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3205132&h=b364386d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3205132</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國「羅斯福號」（CVN 71）和「尼米茲號」（CVN 68）航艦打擊群昨日（21日）在菲律賓海進行聯合演習；同時，「雷根號」（CVN 76）航艦打擊群也在菲律賓海、南海一帶巡弋，美國3個航艦打擊群共同出現此海域，除了威懾中國、北韓，也展現美國貫徹亞太戰略的決心與能力。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，美國太平洋艦隊表示，羅斯福號和尼米茲號航艦打擊群21日在菲律賓海進行聯合演習，內容包含防空、海上監控、海上補給、防禦性空戰、長程打擊等項目。此次聯合演習也展現了美軍獨特的能力，可以在近距離範圍指揮數個航艦打擊群作戰。<br />\n<br />\n羅斯福號指揮官韋里西莫（Doug Verissimo）少將表示，這是演練數個航艦打擊群協同作戰的好機會，尤其在日益緊張的區域情勢，以及武肺疫情（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）的壓力下，我們正在加強戰技與戰備能力。<br />\n<br />\n以日本橫須賀為母港的雷根號在完成維修後，於本月8日離港，重新部署在西太平洋上。根據美國海軍18日公開的照片，雷根號目前也在菲律賓海附近巡弋。<br />\n<br />\n近年來中國海軍的實力不斷增強，在南海以各種手段擴張，展現出取代美國，在亞太建立新秩序的野心，加上北韓翻臉，朝鮮半島情勢緊張，美國3個航艦打擊群此時集結在西太平洋，用意在於警告中國、北韓不可妄動，也向盟國表明，美國對區域安全的承諾。"},{"pid":"9563218a61ac56a32c66a56ed45a5422f054c87a","tid":2074294,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:04:33.000Z","msg":"戰雲密布<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424e261a3b7a5a435e95cbba3a3390e8abad5f8a","tid":2074294,"uid":204039,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:45:21.000Z","msg":"支持派出遼寧艦攻擊美帝航母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f846ccbfea1a8288cffb4b0e64768260fc3c1b4","tid":2074294,"uid":48521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"遼寧輕鬆一挑三<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講緊黑煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6276a8661187be2d07477820eeb4ebd6d0ef9a32","tid":2074294,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:55:18.000Z","msg":"三隻再加埋日本南韓兵力  要同時KO支拿同北韓應該冇難度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce90253fdff6cbbb4f36d48bb7430cf6a6fba574","tid":2074294,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f846ccbfea1a8288cffb4b0e64768260fc3c1b4","tid":2074294,"uid":48521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"遼寧輕鬆一挑三<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講緊黑煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"一隻遼寧艦牽制三支艦隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c318bef400d2338d12796018a4716681a25a7b3","tid":2074294,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:59:29.000Z","msg":"堅哥又要口交啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2facb92c7eed6e4e67ef15fc96526f85e028476","tid":2074294,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce90253fdff6cbbb4f36d48bb7430cf6a6fba574","tid":2074294,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f846ccbfea1a8288cffb4b0e64768260fc3c1b4","tid":2074294,"uid":48521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"遼寧輕鬆一挑三<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講緊黑煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"一隻遼寧艦牽制三支艦隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"